      <p>Flow is designed for personal finance tracking. Users can manually manage income, expense, budget, category, and investment asset records.</p>

      <h2>Financial Responsibility</h2>
      <p>Flow does not provide financial advice or investment advice. The investment screen is only for manual portfolio tracking and does not include trading orders, broker connections, or real-time market data.</p>

      <h2>User Data</h2>
      <p>Users are responsible for the accuracy of the information they enter. Calculated summaries, charts, and insights are based on user-entered data.</p>

      <h2>Export</h2>
      <p>CSV and PDF export features run only when started by the user. The user chooses which app or service to use with shared files.</p>

